OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F349A1782740879
OL,3,CCampaigners angry over lack of
OL,4,Ccriminal charges after iconic pub fire
OL,6,FITV News Central can reveal
OL,7,FStaffordshire Police submitted a file
OL,8,Fof evidence to the CPS on 26 February
OL,9,F2026.
OL,11,FThe CPS said it's still working with
OL,12,Fofficers to clarify the evidence
OL,13,Fprovided.
OL,15,FSix people were arrested during the
OL,16,Finvestigation on suspicion of various
OL,17,Farson-related offences. All have since
OL,18,Fbeen released while enquiries continue.
OL,20,FFor campaigners, the wait is becoming
OL,21,Fincreasingly difficult.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/7
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,350,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F349A1782740879
OL,3,CCampaigners angry over lack of
OL,4,Ccriminal charges after iconic pub fire
OL,6,FPaul Turner, from the Save the Crooked
OL,7,FHouse campaign, said they had expected
OL,8,Fthe investigation to have progressed
OL,9,Fmuch further by now.
OL,11,F"We expected something would have
OL,12,Fhappened. We expected some sort of
OL,13,Fprogress from what happened in 2023,"
OL,14,Fhe said.
OL,16,F"Arrests were made in late 2023, and
OL,17,Fnothing's happened. We don't
OL,18,Funderstand why nobody's been charged."
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/7
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,350,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F349A1782740879
OL,3,CCampaigners angry over lack of
OL,4,Ccriminal charges after iconic pub fire
OL,6,FMr Turner said campaigners had
OL,7,Fstruggled to get updates from either
OL,8,FStaffordshire Police or the CPS.
OL,10,F"Every time we speak to the police,
OL,11,Fthey say speak to the CPS. Every time
OL,12,Fwe speak to the CPS, they say speak to
OL,13,Fthe police. We don't know what's
OL,14,Fhappening," he said.
OL,16,F"We think we are due some sort of
OL,17,Fexplanation. If we had some
OL,18,Finformation as to what's actually
OL,19,Fbeing done properly at the moment.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/7
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,350,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F349A1782740879
OL,3,CCampaigners angry over lack of
OL,4,Ccriminal charges after iconic pub fire
OL,6,F"It just appears to us that it's
OL,7,Fsitting on somebody's desk doing
OL,8,Fnothing.
OL,10,F"We've got no idea if this will take
OL,11,Fanother month or another ten years. I
OL,12,Fthink we are due some sort of
OL,13,Fexplanation."
OL,15,FThe criminal investigation has also
OL,16,Fdelayed efforts to rebuild the pub.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/7
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
