PN,34907
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F349A1782740879
OL,3,CCampaigners angry over lack of
OL,4,Ccriminal charges after iconic pub fire
OL,6,FIts destruction prompted widespread
OL,7,Fcondemnation, with politicians,
OL,8,Fcampaigners and local residents
OL,9,Fcalling for those responsible to be
OL,10,Fheld accountable.
OL,12,FThe Crown Prosecution Service said it
OL,13,Fcontinues to review the evidence
OL,14,Fsubmitted by Staffordshire Police
OL,15,Fbefore deciding whether criminal
OL,16,Fcharges should be brought.
OL,18,FITV News Central asked Staffordshire
OL,19,FPolice about the claims made by the
OL,20,Fcampaigners but haven't had a response.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G7/7
